Conjure your Pact Hourglass in hand until you dismiss it, die, or are more than 5 ft. away from it for 1 min. You can use it as a focus for warlock spells, and it grants you the following:
When not surprised, {{+charisma:modifier}} to initiative rolls;
One per rest when you make an ability check, attack roll, or saving throw, you can choose to reroll before you know if you succeeded.
